title: patch 6.19 unavailable?
body: I woke up today to play some league right? I had to update it to 6.19 no big deal...... but after it updated it wouldn't let me launch and says its unavailable. Anyone else experience this and has found a solution?

replies.body: There was a patch last night, but everything should be okay right now.  Let me know if you still have any issues!
Experiencing the same...no sloutions so far, in fact i was disconnected from a game :/
